OL,6,FA handmade knitted Chris Martin doll,
OL,7,Fsigned by all four members of
OL,8,FColdplay, is helping to raise funds
OL,9,Ffor Dorset and Somerset Air Ambulance.
OL,11,FThe doll was created by Sandra
OL,12,FWitcombe from Somerset to celebrate
OL,13,Fthe band's Glastonbury 2024 headline
