OL,6,FThe doll travelled with Coldplay on
OL,7,Ftheir Music of the Spheres World Tour
OL,8,Fand was filmed sitting in the band's
OL,9,Fdressing room, roaming backstage, and
OL,10,Feven appeared on-stage in Munich.
OL,12,FThe band members, Chris Martin, Jonny
OL,13,FBuckland, Guy Berryman and Will
OL,14,FChampion signed the doll's t-shirt at
OL,15,FWembley Stadium this summer and then
OL,16,Freturned the doll to Sandra, far
OL,17,Fexceeding her original hope of a
OL,18,Fsigned photo.
