OL,6,FSandra has now decided to gift the
OL,7,Fdoll to Dorset and Somerset Air
OL,8,FAmbulance's 2nd Heli Appeal, aimed at
OL,9,Fraising the final #1 million towards a
OL,10,Fsecond helicopter.
OL,12,FThe knitted doll is being offered in a
OL,13,FCrowdfunder Prize Draw and it's hoped
OL,14,Fit'll help towards the charity's
OL,15,Fcampaign.
OL,17,FTracy Bartram, Communications Manager
OL,18,Fat Dorset and Somerset Air Ambulance
OL,19,Fsaid: "We are thrilled to launch our
OL,20,Fvery first Crowdfunder Prize Draw and
OL,21,Fwith such a fantastic item.
